;A Brand New Tiles Experience
Coltas leacagan gu tur ùr


;With Enhanced Tiles and Directory Tiles, Firefox provides users easy access to interesting, relevant content, whether it’s the sites they visit most or new sites for them to discover.
Tha na leacagan leasaichte 's leacagan an eòlaire ann am Firefox a' toirt cothrom furasta dhan luchd-chleachdaidh air susbaint iomchaidh, eadar làraichean air an do thadhal iad is feadhainn a dh'fhaodadh a bhith inntinneach dhaibh.


;What are Tiles?
Dè tha sna leacagan?


;When you open a new tab in Firefox, you see several rectangles that link to different websites.
Nuair a dh'fhosglas tu taba ùr ann am Firefox, chì thu grunn cheàrnagan a tha 'nan ceanglaichean gu làraichean-lìn.


;Some people call them squares, windows or bookmarks; we call them Tiles.
Tha ceàrnagan, uinneagan no fiù comharran-lìn aig cuid orra; 's e leacagan a chanas sinne riutha.


;What are Enhanced Tiles?
Dè tha sna leacagan leasaichte?


;Existing Firefox users will be offered a set of Enhanced Tiles based on their browsing history.
Chì luchd-cleachdaidh aig a bheil Firefox mu thràth grunn leacagan leasaichte a-rèir na h-eachdraidh brabhsaidh aca.


;The Enhanced versions replace the default screenshot with a better image and are displayed only for sites that the user has visited.
Thig an fheadhainn leasaichte an àite nan glacaidhean-sgrìn bunaiteach, le dealbh nas fhearr agus chan fhaighear ann ach làraichean air an robh an cleachdaiche roimhe.


;The improved image is supplied by the site or partner and can include a logo plus a rollover image.
Gheibh sinn na dealbhan leasaichte on làrach no on chom-pàirtiche 's dh'fhaoidte gum faicear suaicheantas no dealbh rollover orra.


;If you frequent Amazon.com, for example, you might see the Amazon logo or icon, instead of a screenshot.
Mar eisimpleir, ma bhios tu air Amazon.co.uk gu tric, dh'fhaoidte gum faic thu suaicheantas no ìomhaigheag Amazon air tè dhiubh seach glacadh-sgrìn.


;What are Directory Tiles?
Dè tha ann an leacagan an eòlaire?


;New Firefox users are initially given a set of Directory Tiles as suggestions for sites that may be of interest to them.
Ma tha cuideigin air ùr-thighinn dha Firefox, gheibh iad grunn leacagan an toiseach air a bheil làraichean a mholamaid dhaibh, 's iad sin leacagan an eòlaire.


;Instead of displaying a blank set of Tiles, Firefox shows content from Mozilla and some Mozilla partners.
An àite leacagan bàna, seallaidh Firefox susbaint dhut o Mozilla is cuid dhe na com-pàirtichean aig Mozilla.


;All partner content is marked as “sponsored” and users have complete control to edit or remove any Tile.
Tha comharra "Sponsairichte" ri dad a thàinig on luchd chom-pàirteachais againn agus tha làn-smachd aig an luchd-cleachdaidh orra 's gabh gin dhiubh a thoirt air falbh.


;Respects your privacy
Suim dha do phrìobhaideachd


;As with all Mozilla products, Tiles provide users with extensive control over their personal data.
Mar gach bathar eile a tha aig Mozilla, bheir na leacagan làn-smachd dhan chleachdaiche a thaobh an dàta phearsanta aca.


;Data collection is limited to the aggregate number of impressions, clicks and Tile placement.
Cha dèid dàta sam bith a chruinneachadh ach suim nan impressions, co mheud briogadh a rinneadh agus càit an deach an cur.


;Nothing is ever personally identifiable. In other words, we don’t know who clicks on what.
Chan aithnichear thu fhèin air gin dheth idir. No ann am facal eile, chan eil spùt againn a thaobh cò tha a' briogadh air dè.


;We just know the total number of views and clicks an individual Tile receives. This helps us deliver the most interesting and relevant content.
Chan fhaic sinne ach co mheud duine a choimhead 's a bhriog air leacag. Leis a sin, bidh e nas fhasa dhuinn susbaint a shealltainn a bhios ùidh aig daoine ann.


;You can deactivate click and impression tracking by clicking on the gear icon on the top right corner of the new tab page, and selecting Classic to show only unenhanced History Tiles or Blank mode.
'S urrainn dhut tracadh nam briogadh 's nan impressions a chur à comas le bhith a' briogadh air dealbh a' ghèar air an taobh deas gu h-àrd air an duilleag ùr 's a' taghadh "Clasaigeach" ann is chan fhaic thu ach leacagan na h-eachdraidh gun leasachadh no feadhainn bhàna.


;Frequently Asked Questions
CÀBHA - Na Ceistean Àbhaisteach


;Are you tracking users now?
A bheil sibh ri tracadh luchd-cleachdaidh a-nis?


;We only collect data from the New Tab page in aggregate form, meaning no data is personally identifiable.
Cha chruinnich sinn o dhuilleagan nan tabaichean ùra ach suim dàta agus is ciall dha sinn nach aithnichear thu gu pearsanta air gin dheth.


;What data is being collected?
Dè seòrsa dàta a thathar 'ga chruinneachadh?


;Aggregate data from the New Tab page includes impressions, clicks and tile placement.
Tha suim an dàta o dhuilleagan nan tabaichean ùra a' gabhail a-steach dàta air impressions, briogaidhean is ionad nan leacagan.


;What data is collected when I opt out?
Dè seòrsa dàta a thèid a chruinneachadh ma bheir mi air falbh an ro-aonta?


;No data is collected when a user chooses to opt out of the enhanced Tiles experience.
Cha dèid dàta sam bith a chruinneachadh nuair a chuireas tu romhad do ro-aonta a thaobh nan leacagan leasaichte a thoirt air falbh.


